    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The Canteen food is very affordable with multiple cuisine options. And it is open throughout the whole day. With multiple Coffee, grocery shops along with an outlet of CCD.",
          "name": "Shikhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports facilities like indoor stadium for basketball, badminton with multiple courts along with a gym. Also it has a laundry system which is free of cost.",
          "name": "Shikhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Everything is good in college only curriculum is not good. So students face problems.  And the old curriculum is what is needed now. Everything else is good.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is study annexe which is availble for student for 24*7 and there is library which has more than 4000 books and many more.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Also when you enter you have to give your i'd to security guard for verification which makes a secure environment inside the campus. Also there is 24*7 security is available.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus is very nice and hostel are very well ventilated and about food i like it because there is some hotel like feeling that you pay at that time and eat. You have not to pay it along sem fee also eat what you want like veg , non veg etc.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the professor are very brilliant and help student time to time for internship till last date and explain all the phenomenon and clear doubt by simply taking a appointment.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Most liked thing that there is no ragging in college and all senior are just like big brother and sister, this thing i so loved. Also there is very much greenery in campus which look very nice mainly in rainy season.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "It is a highly affordable college with fees much lower than other government colleges as well",
          "name": "Atharva Jagdish Shinde",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college provides flexibility of choosing your own subject of interest or specialization.",
          "name": "Atharva Jagdish Shinde",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "There is no seen for placement or internship in industry or in compines. As college is more oriented toward reserch students prefer to do reserch and further studies over industry placement.",
          "name": "Harshvardhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The course curriculum is very rigorous. The faculty teaches in only English,  so if you are not familiar with getting tought by teacher in only English,  you can get difficulty in starting.",
          "name": "Harshvardhan",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Mess food experience is not too bad not too good",
          "name": "Shantanu Kumare",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "It has a night canteen which serves horrible beverages along with little or no option for snacks. And it is also limited as per availability.",
          "name": "Shikhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The gym is strictly time constrained and the trainer is not enough qualified to train the people. It should offer more open hours.",
          "name": "Shikhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "It has a clinic but it doesn’t provide consultations for severe complications and health issues. Also it is restricted to time so it closes everyday after 5 pm.",
          "name": "Shikhar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Students play fire in the hostel for no reason",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The food in the college mess is very bad.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Thing i don't like is the distance of college from pune city is about 10 km which is makes us very deductive for going us to the main pune city. So we go only 2 to 3 time in a month to pune city.",
          "name": "Vivek Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college does force you to study subjects like HSS, ECS where they teach sanskrit and earth sciences in first sem which might not be very useful in the future.",
          "name": "Atharva Jagdish Shinde",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
